Translingual

[edit]

Etymology

[edit]

From Dugong +‎ -idae.

Proper noun

[edit]

Dugongidae

A taxonomic family within the order Sirenia – dugong.

Hypernyms

[edit]

(family): Eukaryota – superkingdom; Animalia – kingdom; Bilateria – subkingdom; Deuterostomia – infrakingdom; Chordata – phylum; Vertebrata – subphylum; Gnathostomata – infraphylum; Tetrapoda – superclass; Mammalia – class; Trechnotheria - subclass; Zatheria - infraclass; Epitheria - magnorder; Afrotheria - superorder; Sirenia - order

Hyponyms

[edit]

(family): Dugong (sole extant genus)
